name: Tamessa Compton
text: My husband and I just moved back to Gadsden January of 2021.  WE moved here from Florida.  WE are both originally from Gadsden.  I was a karaoke KJ in Florida for 3 years and saw a sign that they were having it that Friday so we decided to go.  Wow!  The people welcomed us with open arms and sat at our table, introduced themselves and entertained us all night long.  The music was great and the Karaoke KJ was great as well.  The sound system was top notch.  I couldn't get over how friendly everyone was.  Wait, yes I can this is Gadsden, Alabama after all.  We both want to to say thank you for a wonderful time and we will definitely be coming back.  Keep up the good work and you will have many more new people coming to your establishment.  I truly believe that kindness and friendliness is the key to success!!!!
